OL,3,CNRW urge people to check flood risk
OL,4,Cand 'be ready' as winter approaches
OL,6,FNatural Resources Wales (NRW) is
OL,7,Fencouraging people across Wales to
OL,8,Fcheck their flood risk online, sign up
OL,9,Ffor free flood warnings and know what
OL,10,Fto do if flooding is forecast in their
OL,11,Farea this winter.
OL,13,F1 in 7 homes and businesses in Wales
OL,14,Fare at risk of flooding and, as the
OL,15,Fclimate warms, there are warnings that
OL,16,Fthe number of extreme weather events
OL,17,Fwill increase.
