OL,3,CNRW urge people to check flood risk
OL,4,Cand 'be ready' as winter approaches
OL,6,FIn the 2023-24 period, Wales was hit
OL,7,Fby 12 named storms, the highest number
OL,8,Fsince 2015, with last winter and
OL,9,Fautumn being particularly wet and
OL,10,Fwindy.
OL,12,FThe body is also urging those who live
OL,13,Fin areas at risk of flooding, who have
OL,14,Fnot experienced flooding before, to
OL,15,Ftake action now to help protect their
OL,16,Fhome, possessions and family from the
OL,17,Fdevastating effect of flooding in the
OL,18,Ffuture.
