OL,3,CNRW urge people to check flood risk
OL,4,Cand 'be ready' as winter approaches
OL,6,FNRW operate more than 400 monitoring
OL,7,Fstations across Wales provide live
OL,8,Friver level, rainfall and tidal data,
OL,9,Fall of which is used to issue flood
OL,10,Fwarnings to people living or working
OL,11,Fin flood risk areas.
OL,13,FThey issue Flood Alerts and Warnings
OL,14,Fif rivers and coasts reach levels at
OL,15,Fwhich flooding is possible or
OL,16,Fexpected, with teams monitoring and
OL,17,Fforecasting river and sea levels
OL,18,Faround Wales 24 hours a day.
OL,20,FThere are three levels of flood
OL,21,Fwarnings:
