OL,3,CNRW urge people to check flood risk
OL,4,Cand 'be ready' as winter approaches
OL,6,FJeremy Parr, head of flood and
OL,7,Fincident risk management at NRW said:
OL,8,F"So often we hear the words, 'It won't
OL,9,Fhappen to me,' but when it comes to
OL,10,Fflooding, that mindset can have
OL,11,Fdevastating consequences.
OL,13,F"Flooding can devastate homes, disrupt
OL,14,Flivelihoods, and leave lasting impacts
OL,15,Fon mental health and wellbeing.
OL,17,F"While we don't know what the weather
OL,18,Fwill bring us this winter, will we all
OL,19,Fneed to be ready to take action
OL,20,Fwherever it is needed.
