OL,3,CNRW urge people to check flood risk
OL,4,Cand 'be ready' as winter approaches
OL,6,F"As we launch our Be Flood Ready week
OL,7,Fin Wales, we're urging everyone to
OL,8,Ftake proactive steps to protect
OL,9,Fyourselves and your loved ones from
OL,10,Fthat risk.
OL,12,F"Start by checking your flood risk on
OL,13,Four website and, if you find you are
OL,14,Fat risk, sign up to our free flood
OL,15,Fwarning service and create a flood
OL,16,Fplan."
