OL,3,CNRW urge people to check flood risk
OL,4,Cand 'be ready' as winter approaches
OL,6,FA Met Office spokesperson said: "Being
OL,7,Fprepared for severe weather is the
OL,8,Fbest way of minimising any impacts.
OL,9,FJust a few simple steps can help
OL,10,Fhouseholds to manage disruptive
OL,11,Fweather as much as possible and
OL,12,Fprevent short and long term impacts.
OL,14,F"Checking your flood risk and signing
OL,15,Fup for flood alerts as well as weather
OL,16,Fwarnings is a good first step in being
OL,17,Fas prepared as possible for the
OL,18,Fimpacts the weather may bring in the
OL,19,Fcoming months."
